Again&s;t &s;uffering the&s;e to gain
<PB N="283" REF="292">
po&s;&s;e&s;&s;ion of the heart, admonition is
&s;carcely nece&s;&s;ary. But I mu&s;t admoni&s;h
you, that even tho&s;e which are accounted
