<PB N="406" REF="415">
their own choice, they join in the
vices of the libertine; that they may not
be reproached as per&s;ons of a narrow
mind, and &s;till en&s;laved to the prejudices
of education. How much rea&s;on is there
to believe theat, merely from this timidity
