his &s;oul</HI><NOTE N="&ast;" PLACE="foot">Wi&s;dom of Solomon iv. 11.</NOTE>. When Sodom could not
furni&s;h ten righreous men to &s;ave it, <HI>Lot</HI>
remained un&s;potted amid&s;t the contagion.
He lived like an angel among &s;pirits of
darkne&s;s; and the de&s;troying flame was not
